OL,3,CLabour to reform Ofgem to give more
OL,4,Cprotections after energy bills crisis
OL,6,FHouseholds will be offered more
OL,7,Fprotections and better customer
OL,8,Fservice from energy providers as part
OL,9,Fof plans by the Labour government to
OL,10,Freform the regulator Ofgem.
OL,12,FThe watchdog could get new consumer-
OL,13,Ffacing powers including shortening the
OL,14,Feight-week mandatory response time
OL,15,Fwhen people complain to their energy
OL,16,Fsupplier.
OL,18,FCustomers could also get better access
OL,19,Fto automatic compensation when things
OL,20,Fgo wrong with their energy bills.
