OL,3,CLabour to reform Ofgem to give more
OL,4,Cprotections after energy bills crisis
OL,6,FMinisters say they want to rebuild
OL,7,Ftrust in the sector after energy price
OL,8,Fspikes in 2022 led to soaring bills
OL,9,Fand caused a swathe of smaller
OL,10,Fsuppliers to go bust.
OL,12,FLarger companies have faced
OL,13,Faccusations of profiteering off the
OL,14,Fsharp increase in wholesale costs
OL,15,Fcaused by Russia's invasion of Ukraine.
OL,17,FMany of the biggest energy companies
OL,18,Fthat provide heat and electricity to
OL,19,FBritish homes have reported record
OL,20,Fprofits in recent years.
