OL,3,CLabour to reform Ofgem to give more
OL,4,Cprotections after energy bills crisis
OL,6,FOfficials said the Ofgem reforms would
OL,7,Ffocus on improvements to the bill-
OL,8,Fpaying and complaints process.
OL,10,FThe review will also look into how
OL,11,FOfgem can address wider issues like
OL,12,Fmaking homes more energy efficient
OL,13,Fwith things like heat pumps and solar
OL,14,Fpanels.
OL,16,FOfgem chief executive Jonathan
OL,17,FBrearley welcomed the review, adding
OL,18,Fthat "a great deal" has changed since
OL,19,Fthe regulator's remit was set out 25
OL,20,Fyears ago.
