OL,6,FHe said the recent crisis was "an
OL,7,Fimportant reminder to all that
OL,8,Fprotecting consumers must remain the
OL,9,Ffocus no matter what challenges we
OL,10,Fface".
OL,12,FLabour set out sweeping plans for how
OL,13,Fit will decarbonise the grid by 2030
OL,14,Fearlier in December.
OL,16,FThey include measures to speed up
OL,17,Fplanning decisions on clean energy
OL,18,Fprojects and free up the queue for
OL,19,Fprojects to get a connection to the
OL,20,Fgrid, which is currently seeing some
OL,21,Fschemes held up for years.
