OL,3,CLabour to reform Ofgem to give more
OL,4,Cprotections after energy bills crisis
OL,6,FThe review of Ofgem will also examine
OL,7,Fthe regulator's role in approving new
OL,8,Finfrastructure projects like wind and
OL,9,Fsolar farms, and in bringing down the
OL,10,Fgrid queue.
OL,12,FLabour has faced criticism in recent
OL,13,Fmonths for restricting winter fuel
OL,14,Fpayments to those receiving pension
OL,15,Fcredit.
OL,17,FIt means around 10 million people will
OL,18,Flose out this winter, with the benefit
OL,19,Ftaken away from all but the poorest
OL,20,Fpensioners in the country. About 11.5
OL,21,Fmillion people used to receive it.
